Package: icy
Title: Interface for Configuration using YAML
Version: 0.1.20
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Peeters", 
           email = "benjamin.peeters@pik-potsdam.de", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = ""))
Description: Provides an interface for managing configuration in R packages using 
    YAML files. This package enables R packages to easily configure and manage 
    environment variables, settings, and preferences through YAML configuration files,
    supporting both interactive setup and automated workflows.
